The paper deals with the enumeration of chordless cycles in a graph, which is a problem in graph theory. The use of vertex labeling and initial valid vertex triplet suggests that the paper may belong to the category of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM). The algorithmic approach and the use of breadth-first search suggest that the paper may also belong to the categories of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Computational Geometry (cs.CG). The time complexity analysis suggests that the paper may belong to the category of Machine Learning (cs.DL) or Game Theory (cs.GT), as these fields often deal with algorithms and complexity analysis.
